video.title: 1:23 Video Trailer
video.description: A video preview for Synchronicity's production of 1:23 by Carson Kreitzer. Now playing at 7 Stages (1105 Euclid Ave, Atlanta 30307) through May 17, Thurs-Sat @ 8p, Sun @ 7p. Featuring Suehyla El-Attar, Rachel Garner, Dori Garziano, Mark Gray, Daniel Thomas May, and Theroun Patterson. Directed by Rachel May. Video edited by Ashby Wratchford. More info & tickets at www.synchrotheatre.com.
